{"tid":524962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山西臨汾大教堂遭公安炸毀      教會牧師拒絕加入官方三自教會","createTime":"2018-01-10T06:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T07:33:46.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cf270c8caa662dd9494935172608910c840c084b","tid":524962,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T06:54:05.000Z","msg":"【山西臨汾大教堂遭公安炸毀】<br />\n     【教會牧師拒絕加入官方三自教會】<br />\n<br />\n星期二上午，山西臨汾市派出大批防暴武警進駐該市金燈台大教堂，先把教徒軟禁在家，然後用炸藥炸毀教堂地基，然後拆毀整座教堂。<br />\n<br />\n早於2009年，政府已開始游說金燈台教堂楊榮麗牧師及其妻子，加入官方的三自教會，由宗教部門直接管理，但遭他們多次拒絕，及後他們被判七年勞教，2016年才獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n今次臨汾市是以商業發展用地為理由，清拆金燈台教堂。<br />\n金燈堂教堂現有信眾五百多人。<br />\n<br />\n#拆教堂<br />\n#山西臨汾<br />\n#宗教自由<br />\n#有線中國組<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/posts/1607816352696178\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fposts%2F1607816352696178&d=FpeAYFKsRB0rqWTOSL4xgzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=2929b47f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/posts/1607816352696178</a>"},{"pid":"687c5114753089b022c4b47c7c1ecbd39e5ee51a","tid":524962,"uid":9726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T07:25:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fd1f37cdacbb1f89dfa5149366de38f5283ea2b","tid":524962,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T07:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/26196334_1607816259362854_3378600180847192701_n.jpg?oh=a124bb2b93cf5a7cb4aef2c874d4899d&amp;oe=5AF09E6A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F26196334_1607816259362854_3378600180847192701_n.jpg%3Foh%3Da124bb2b93cf5a7cb4aef2c874d4899d%26oe%3D5AF09E6A&h=f0454fa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/26220027_1607816269362853_695203522174043_n.jpg?oh=d50939a3226f89839efa754e1878958f&amp;oe=5AF4889A\" data-thumbnail-sr